 the scale of\nbeyond-MSSM physics, even in case the extended gauge group is broken at an\nenergy beyond the reach of the LHC.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Jan 2013 16:39:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-04-17"}
