i\nsurface. Most of the numerical results can be understood quantitatively from\nthe ansatz, which provides a simple picture for the nature of the SDW states.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Jan 2013 22:35:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-20"}
