ion of a relative entropy\nwhich plays the role of a Lyapunov functional.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 26 Jan 2013 11:17:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Mar 2013 13:45:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-03-08"}
